# .github/CODEOWNERS
#
# Mechanizes the directory ownership + veto authority table per
# docs/methodology/multi-agent-pr-workflow.md §Roles.
# Ratified by ADR-023 Phase 1 (mission-45).
#
# Handle convention: GitHub teams @apnex-org/architect + @apnex-org/engineer
# (Option A per thread-272 2026-04-23). Teams are created by the Director
# in the mission-45 admin window bundled with branch protection (T2) +
# merge queue enablement (T3). This file is inert until that activation.
#
# Org-migration note (thread-274 2026-04-23): the repo was transferred from
# the Director's individual account (apnex) to a new GitHub org (apnex-org)
# during the T2/T3 admin window — individual accounts cannot host teams.
# Handles prefix to @apnex-org/<role>; the 14-row ownership spec is unchanged.
#
# GitHub CODEOWNERS semantics: the LAST matching pattern wins.
# Broadest patterns first; specificity increases downward.

# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# Catch-all fallback — surfaces not named below require co-author sign-off.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------
*                                     @apnex-org/architect @apnex-org/engineer

# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# Architect-owned (Primary owner + Veto authority: Architect)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------
/docs/methodology/                    @apnex-org/architect
/docs/reviews/                        @apnex-org/architect
/docs/planning/                       @apnex-org/architect
/docs/decisions/                      @apnex-org/architect

# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# Engineer-owned (Primary owner + Veto authority: Engineer)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------
/docs/traces/                         @apnex-org/engineer

# Code surface
/hub/src/                             @apnex-org/engineer
# mission-83 W6-narrowed: substrate-architect ownership for the storage-substrate
# module (HubStorageSubstrate + SchemaDef reconciler + LISTEN/NOTIFY watch primitive).
# More specific pattern wins per GitHub CODEOWNERS semantics.
/hub/src/storage-substrate/           @apnex-org/architect @apnex-org/engineer
/adapters/*/src/                      @apnex-org/engineer
/packages/*/src/                      @apnex-org/engineer

# Test surface (includes invariant tests)
/hub/test/                            @apnex-org/engineer
/adapters/*/test/                     @apnex-org/engineer
/packages/*/test/                     @apnex-org/engineer

# Operational scripts
/hub/scripts/                         @apnex-org/engineer
/adapters/*/scripts/                  @apnex-org/engineer

# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# Shared (Co-author sign-off required — both approvals needed)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------
/docs/audits/                         @apnex-org/architect @apnex-org/engineer
/docs/specs/                          @apnex-org/architect @apnex-org/engineer
/.github/workflows/                   @apnex-org/architect @apnex-org/engineer

# Root configs — cross-package effects
/package.json                         @apnex-org/architect @apnex-org/engineer
/package-lock.json                    @apnex-org/architect @apnex-org/engineer
/tsconfig.json                        @apnex-org/architect @apnex-org/engineer
/vitest.config.ts                     @apnex-org/architect @apnex-org/engineer

# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# docs/missions/ — mixed-by-file per §Directory ownership.
# Ordered most-specific last per CODEOWNERS precedence rules.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------
/docs/missions/                       @apnex-org/architect @apnex-org/engineer
/docs/missions/*-preflight.md         @apnex-org/architect
/docs/missions/*-kickoff-decisions.md @apnex-org/architect
/docs/missions/*-merge.md             @apnex-org/engineer

# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# Explicitly NOT covered here (by design):
#
# - start-*.sh, architect-chat.sh, scripts/local/ and other
#   session-local files must not land on main at all. CODEOWNERS
#   is review-routing; it does not prevent files from landing.
#   That enforcement lives in secret-scan CI (T4) + pre-commit
#   hook (T5), not here.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------
